PLUS is a boutique global sports and entertainment advisory, specialising in helping businesses to harness the power of sports & entertainment.

We help brands, rights holders, investors, and elite talent through sponsorship acquisition, M&A, talent acquisition, investments in sport and entertainment.

Our core services include:
- Brand partnership strategy, advising brands on how and where to invest in sponsorship based on business objectives; 
- Brokering integrated supply-led partnerships;  
- Naming rights and other big-ticket sponsorships;
- Sponsorship strategy including rights packaging, brokering, go-to-market, narrative and activation.

